      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride and it's looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, inside and out! It drives like a dream and has plenty of adventures left in it. If you're looking for a dependable set of wheels that\u2019s been well-loved, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
