    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2003 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit exhibits crisp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise gate entry, paired with a healthy clutch. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, and the VANOS system has been serviced to ensure long-term timing reliability. Riding on a sorted suspension with refreshed control arm bushings, this M3 delivers the analog feedback and lateral grip enthusiasts crave. It is a turn-key performance machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
