    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular oil changes. Clean title. Minor surface scratches. Mechanically sound. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk\u2014typical for a car that has enjoyed the open road but was always parked with care. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is clean and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat. Every button, dial, and digital display functions perfectly, from the crisp premium audio system to the ice-cold dual-zone climate control. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a comprehensive service history. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, a new cabin air filter, and a brake pad replacement within the last 3,000 miles. The tires provide excellent grip with significant tread life remaining. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a rattle-free experience. It is a reliable, honest vehicle that has been maintained to a high standard and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
