    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable, smooth drive without any of the 'new car' stress. It still looks great and handles like a dream! I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
