    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is powered by the 3.8L M97 flat-six, featuring VarioCam Plus for a broad torque curve and a visceral 7,200 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise G97 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis benefits from Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing exceptional lateral stability and damping control. Recent preventative maintenance includes an IMS bearing inspection and updated water pump, ensuring the cooling system and valvetrain are track-ready. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and hydraulic steering feedback remain razor-sharp. A superb example for the purist seeking analog engagement.",
